# Class: <http://purl.bioontology.org/ontology/EMRO_0000011> (increased heart response to emotion)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.bioontology.org/ontology/EMRO_0000011> "A heart process during which the rate at which the heart beats increases as a response to an emotion process.")
