# Class: <http://purl.bioontology.org/ontology/EMRO_0000013> (cognitive response to emotion)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.bioontology.org/ontology/EMRO_0000013> "A cognitive process that happens as a response to an emotion process.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.bioontology.org/ontology/EMRO_0000013> <https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9625-1899>)
